## 🎮 Enhanced: "How to Play Orthoplay" Section

This PR expands the onboarding guide for new users by:

- ✅ Adding a full walkthrough of gameplay
- ✅ Including step-by-step instructions
- ✅ Adding 3-step visual images
- ✅ Providing tips and examples
- ✅ CTA to begin playing right after

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">🎮 What is Orthoplay?</h2>
<p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
Orthoplay is a fast-paced, word-based puzzle game where players arrange scrambled letters to form correct English words before time runs out. Each correct word earns points. The faster you solve, the more you score!
</p>
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">📝 How to Play: Step-by-Step</h2>
<ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-3">
  <li><strong>Start a New Game:</strong> Click “Play Now” to launch a new session.</li>
  <li><strong>See the Scrambled Word:</strong> You’ll see jumbled letters on the screen like <code>B A N L K</code>.</li>
  <li><strong>Drag & Drop or Type:</strong> Rearrange the letters to form a valid word like <strong>BLANK</strong>.</li>
  <li><strong>Submit Your Answer:</strong> Press Enter or tap Submit to lock your answer.</li>
  <li><strong>Timer is Ticking:</strong> You have <strong>30 seconds</strong> for each word. Score more by being quick!</li>
  <li><strong>Streak Bonus:</strong> Solving multiple words in a row increases your multiplier bonus.</li>
</ol>
