<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">💡 Pro Tips</h3>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
  <li>Look for common prefixes and suffixes (e.g., “-ing”, “re-”)</li>
  <li>Use the shuffle button if you’re stuck</li>
  <li>Typing is faster than dragging on desktop!</li>
  <li>Don’t guess – incorrect attempts cost time!</li>
</ul>
